    "content": "<div id=\"floorcontent\" class=\"b-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-80c9ee8c=\"\">\n<p class=\"editorContent\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" data-v-80c9ee8c=\"\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'SF Pro SC', 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Icons', 'PingFang SC', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'; font-size: 10pt; white-space: pre-wrap; float: none; display: inline;\">尊敬的商家朋友：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'SF Pro SC', 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Icons', 'PingFang SC', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'; white-space: pre-wrap; float: none; display: inline;\"> 您好！为切实保障消费者权益及商家自主经营，进一步优化消费者与商家自主协商解决问题中的责任分配，现对《京东开放平台个人/个体交易管理规则》及相关规则进行修订。修订公示期：2025年4月22日- 2025年4月29日，规则预计于2025年4月30日生效。公示期满将另行发布正式生效规则。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'SF Pro SC', 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Icons', 'PingFang SC', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'; white-space: pre-wrap; float: none; display: inline;\"> 修订内容主要针对退货、退款场景，明确退货、退款场景下的处置。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'SF Pro SC', 'SF Pro Display', 'SF Pro Icons', 'PingFang SC', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, 'Noto Sans', sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol', 'Noto Color Emoji'; white-space: pre-wrap; float: none; display: inline;\"><img class=\"wscnph\" src=\"//img30.360buyimg.com/venderrule//jfs/t1/271492/1/26857/108464/680b6c98F92c3e53d/1b5bdda3a216c80e.png\" width=\"600\" /></span></span></p>\n</div>",
